6. Reverse String
s[::-1]

Output:

"nohtyp"

Important for interviews.

7. Step Size

Syntax:

s[start:end:step]

Example:

s[::2]

Output:

"pto"

Because it jumps every 2 characters.

8. Frequently Used Interview Slices
Slice	Meaning
s[:]	copy string
s[::-1]	reverse
s[:-1]	remove last char
s[1:]	remove first char
s[:k]	first k chars
s[k:]	after k index
9. Quick Memory Trick
[start : end]

Think:

start included
end excluded

Very important rule.